</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></conbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-413D000D-1733-4578-95D7-CBC36AC62908.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool><link keyref="04FUNC01" class="- topic/link " href="GUID-7B53C9E2-D13D-4E0F-AA3E-D319EC11427A.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">04 Overview of the components of the printhead</linktext></link></related-links></concept>